overview: Syuhada, a naive has agreed to go hiking with her friends in Bukit Damai over the weekend. However, on the day of the incident, Syuhada felt strange when his friend did not show up. Assuming his friend had started the climb, she went into the forest and walked alone. Unfortunately, she fell into a hole which was 15 feet deep and not unable to get out of the hole.
title: Survival 486
